{% call getstarted.section("Overview") -%}

  <p>Icons are small visual representations that help us depict a variety of ideas, technologies, and interactions. Our icons are open and straightforward, just like our brand. This library includes a set of brand icons and a set of UI icons. To see the repo of brand icons, visit <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1SRhy8-bYBgaA3Jsi1t_Fxz-Yo9ORgdRy5Kec9hg_wSM/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">this page</a>. To see the repo of UI icons, visit <a href="https://xd.adobe.com/view/6baa8747-360f-4eb4-b9e0-33a03fc20630-3ef9/screen/a1c3a8ae-00ef-403d-a8d2-9e635ff4d875" target="_blank">this page</a>.</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Brand icons</strong> - Large icons that represent general and technical concepts</li>
    <li><strong>UI icons</strong> - Small icons used for interactions or states within website or product interface components</li>
  </ul>

{%- endcall %}

{% call getstarted.section("Get started") -%}

  <p>Available brand and UI icons can be accessed in the Libraries panel in Adobe XD. You can search for an icon by name or by expanding any corresponding section.</p>

  {% call getstarted.example(palette='lightest') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/getstarted/icon-library/icon-library-getting-started.svg' | url }}" alt="Getting started with brand/UI icons" style="--example-img-max-width: 255px;">
  {%- endcall %}

{%- endcall %}

{% call getstarted.section("Adobe XD") -%}

