{% call getstarted.section("Usage") -%}

  <h4>Brand icons</h4>

  <p>Use brand icons to represent general and technical concepts, their recommended size is between 32px and 96px.</p>

  {% call getstarted.example(palette='lightest') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/getstarted/icon-library/icon-library-icon-examples-brand.svg' | url }}" alt="Brand icon examples" style="--example-img-max-width: 872px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>UI icons</h4>

  <p>Use UI icons to represent interactions or states within website or product interface components. UI icons come in various sizes depending on what component they are used in.</p>

  {% call getstarted.example(palette='lightest') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/getstarted/icon-library/icon-library-icon-examples-ui.svg' | url }}" alt="UI icon examples" style="--example-img-max-width: 872px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Component states</h4>

  <p>Use Component States in XD to toggle between different colors, interactions, or states.</p>

