  <h4>Brand icon sizing</h4>

  <p>This library is set up so that all brand icons have a height or width of 64px. When using icons in your designs, some of them will appear smaller or larger than others. You might need to <strong>visually</strong> adjust them so they have similar proportions when used in close proximity to each other.</p>

  {% call getstarted.example(palette='lightest') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/getstarted/icon-library/icon-library-icon-sizing-brand.svg' | url }}" alt="Brand icon sizing" style="--example-img-max-width: 344px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>UI icon sizing</h4>

  <p>If you need different icon sizes when creating a new component, most UI icons include Small and Large versions.</p>

