{% call getstarted.section("Frequently asked questions") -%}

  <p><strong>When are new icons added to this library?</strong><br />New brand assets are released every month, so any new brand icons will be added within one day. When a new design system component is created, any new UI icons will also be added within one day.</p>

  <hr class="margin-top--4 margin-bottom--4">

  <p><strong>How do I request a new icon?</strong><br />To request a new brand icon, contact the <a href="mailto:brand@redhat.com">Brand team</a>. To request a new UI icon, contact the <a href="mailto:digital-design-system@redhat.com">Design system team</a>.</p>

  <hr class="margin-top--4 margin-bottom--4">

  <p><strong>How do I request an existing icon be added to this library?</strong><br />If your desired brand or UI icon is <strong>not</strong> found in this library, check if it exists in the <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1SRhy8-bYBgaA3Jsi1t_Fxz-Yo9ORgdRy5Kec9hg_wSM/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">brand icon repo</a> or <a href="https://xd.adobe.com/view/6baa8747-360f-4eb4-b9e0-33a03fc20630-3ef9/screen/a1c3a8ae-00ef-403d-a8d2-9e635ff4d875" target="_blank">UI icon repo</a> first. If the icon does exist in those repos but not in this library, contact the <a href="mailto:digital-design-system@redhat.com">Design system team</a> and it will be added within one day.</p>

  <hr class="margin-top--4 margin-bottom--4">

  <p><strong>Why is a brand or UI icon no longer available?</strong><br />It might have been removed if brand assets or design system components were deprecated. To find out more, contact the <a href="mailto:brand@redhat.com">Brand team</a> for missing brand icons or the <a href="mailto:digital-design-system@redhat.com">Design system team</a> for missing UI icons.</p>

